summary: The document is a CIA information telegram dated July 18, 1963, concerning Vietnam, which is part of the National Security Files, Box 198. It discusses military problems and the war in Vietnam, and was last reviewed on October 9, 2000. This record is related to the President John F. Kennedy Assassination Records Act of 1992.
